HEADWORD: old-fashioned
<hw>old-fashioned</hw></mhw> <pos>n.</pos>
<def>A cocktail consisting of whiskey, bitters, and sugar, garnished
with with fruit slices and often a cherry.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

